    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281610/extras/2ee2b13d7439d6f5a2f24ca2fe695e42.poster.avif?t=1767186567\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281610/extras/2ee2b13d7439d6f5a2f24ca2fe695e42.webm?t=1767186567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281610/extras/2ee2b13d7439d6f5a2f24ca2fe695e42.mp4?t=1767186567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不太遥远的未来，人类终于跨过了深渊的边缘：世界在废墟中，少数幸存者不仅要相互斗争，还要应对在废土上肆虐的无数新生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经过多年的奴役，你终于设法逃脱。现在是时候报复你的折磨者，攀升到顶端：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越变异怪物、僵尸、外星人、机器人等一切的大军，每个关卡的尽头都有一个无情的boss等待你的惩罚，带着你可以拿走的宝贵战利品。每个新的身体部位都会给你一个强大的主动技能，每次运行都让你创建一个你喜欢的新的独特构建。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但要小心：一瞬间的疏忽可能轻易地让你失去生命 - 你的旅程将从头开始！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281610/extras/34ceaf5afd6be816db187e07af922e25.poster.avif?t=1767186567\" width=240 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281610/extras/34ceaf5afd6be816db187e07af922e25.webm?t=1767186567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281610/extras/34ceaf5afd6be816db187e07af922e25.mp4?t=1767186567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特性</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集废料在关卡之间购买或升级物品或身体部位</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对抗40多种不同类型的敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在九个不同主题中产生过程生成的关卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数百个独特的身体部位和物品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集XP以解锁永久升级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单的难度模式，自动瞄准</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >极度优化，即使在较旧的硬件上也能运行良好和美观</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本地合作（也可与远程共同游玩功能配合使用）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281610/extras/e74543df5094f1879b68d33544706815.avif?t=1767186567\" width=780 height=240 /></span></p>",
